# Docker build context excludes (context = repo root for all infra/docker/*.Dockerfile).
# Keep the context small and never ship secrets or rebuildable artifacts into an image.

# VCS, editors, agent + docs (not needed to build any image)
.git
.github
.idea
.vscode
.claude
docs

# Dependencies & build outputs — reinstalled / regenerated inside the image
**/node_modules
**/dist
**/.next
**/.turbo
apps/api/generated

# Secrets & env — never copied into images
**/.env
**/.env.*

# Infra itself is not COPYed into app images...
infra
# ...EXCEPT the zitadel-bootstrap script, which infra/docker/zitadel-bootstrap.Dockerfile COPYs into
# its own tiny image (ADR-0043 Phase 3). The Dockerfiles themselves are read by the daemon, not COPYed.
!infra/scripts
!infra/scripts/zitadel-bootstrap.sh

# Logs & OS cruft
**/*.log
.DS_Store
